      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "‚ÄúThese may appear like obscure, arcane rules to most,‚Äù said Josh Zinner, CEO of the Interfaith Center on Corporate Responsibility. ‚ÄúBut their actual impact is significant, because companies are using these rules to stifle investor conversation about critical long-term risks like climate change.‚Äù",
