      {
        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p><em><u><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Proposed%20new%20SEC%20rules%20could%20give%20activist%20shareholders%20more%20power%20than%20ever%20before%20%E2%80%94%20but%20will%20it%20be%20enough%20to%20shift%20corporate%20behavior%3F%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levernews.com%2Fbiden-gives-activist-shareholders-a-leg-up%2F%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dlink%26utm_campaign%3Dtw-prefill\">Click to share this article on Twitter</a></strong></u></em></p>"
      },
      {
        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p><em><strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levernews.com%2Fbiden-gives-activist-shareholders-a-leg-up%2F&amp;amp;src=sdkpreparse\">Click to share this article on Facebook</a></strong></em></p>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The rules would make it harder for companies to block shareholder resolutions, which are requests that people or groups who own stock in companies can put to a vote of all shareholders at a company‚Äôs annual meeting, by removing several of the justifications that companies can currently use to block resolutions from coming to a vote. While they‚Äôre not binding, resolutions that win majority support are generally taken seriously by corporate boards, since the shareholders that vote for resolutions can also vote to replace board members if they don‚Äôt take action.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The practice of using resolutions to prod companies into taking steps to advance environmental and social goals has ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "spiked",
